data.meta_description: Edwin O. Smith High School’s Cheryl Granger, coach, Robert Kao, Richard Kao, Eric Barrett, Ron LaMonica and Harrison Hall of Storrs, Connecticut, pose for a team photo during the 2015 National Science Bowl competition, Thursday, April 30, 2015, in Washington, DC.
